Subject: drm/amdgpu: move lockdep assert to the right place.
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: d7d7ddc15672940be0dbbe03e016c5bb617256b8
Patch-mainline: v5.18-rc1
References: jsc#PED-1166 jsc#PED-1168 jsc#PED-1170 jsc#PED-1218 jsc#PED-1220 jsc#PED-1222 jsc#PED-1223 jsc#PED-1225

Since newly added BOs don't have any mappings it's ok to add them
without holding the VM lock. Only when we add per VM BOs the lock is
mandatory.

